    "faq_zhAACx": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "question_XamVPH": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>Causes</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Arch pain, also known as arch strain, involves inflammation and/or a burning sensation at the arch of the foot. Various factors can cause arch pain, including structural imbalances or foot injuries<br/><br/>The most common cause of arch pain is Plantar Fasciitis, a condition affecting the plantar fascia, a fibrous tissue band running from the heel to the forefoot.<br/><br/>If untreated and strain on the longitudinal arch continues, a heel spur, a bony protrusion, may develop. Prompt treatment is essential to prevent the condition from worsening.<br/></p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_x9EPUx": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>Treatment and Prevention</strong>",
            "text": "<p><strong>GET STRETCHING EXERCISE GUIDE</strong><br/>Our Plantar Fasciitis Kit comes with an exercise guide that helps give you instructions on how to stretch the plantar fascia as well as the muscles and tendons surrounding the tissue. In turn it can help with reducing tension and putting you on the path towards pain relief. </p><p><br/><br/><strong>SHOP RECOMMENDED ORTHOTICS</strong><br/>If arch pain is related to overpronation (flat feet), use an orthotic with a medial heel post and adequate arch support. This type of orthotic helps control over-pronation, supports the arch, and provides relief from pain. If the problem persists, consult your foot doctor.</p><p><br/><br/><strong>SHOP RECOMMENDED SHOES</strong><br/>Avoid high-heeled shoes whenever possible to prevent exacerbating arch pain. Opt for footwear with a reasonable heel height, soft uppers, shock-absorbing soles, and proper arch support.Shoes with a wide toe box are recommended to reduce pressure on the bunion.<br/><br/></p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "question_XamVPH",
        "question_x9EPUx"
      ],
